been getting check errors on all platforms for a while now.

I had recently upgraded the necessary utility JAR (Juicer Tools) managed
with a BiocFileCache entry and looks like the machines are still using an
old version as a result of that caching, so could you please remove the
associated BiocFileCache folder for this package on the build machines?
This way, the correct version that doesn't error out on the check gets
downloaded.

